data.description: 3.75% INTEREST RATE WITH ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN!!  Built in 2020 home with SOLAR PANELS!! Modern Elegance at its Finest! Step into this stunning 2020 open floor plan home and be captivated by the seamless blend of style and functionality. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this architectural masterpiece is a true testament to contemporary design. The master bedroom offers a sizeable walk-in closet, providing ample space for all your wardrobe essentials. As you make your way through the home, the sleek tile flooring in the kitchen, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances create an inviting atmosphere perfect for culinary adventures. Retreat to the cozy living room and bedrooms adorned with plush carpeting that adds warmth and comfort to every step. The bathrooms feature elegant laminate flooring, adding a touch of sophistication to your daily routine. Step outside to a covered porch and a fully fenced backyard for just the right amount of privacy. $35,000 worth of solar panels for extremely low energy bills. This remarkable property is more than just a house; it's an embodiment of modern living at its finest. Centrally located, close to shopping, dining, and schools. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity!
